1 A BILL for an Act to create and enact a new section to chapter 28-01 of the North Dakota
2 Century Code, relating to time limitations for serving an answer to a claim.
3 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
4 SECTION 1. A new section to chapter 28-01 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
5 and enacted as follows:
6 Answer - Time limitation.
7 Notwithstanding any other provision of law, a defendant shall serve an answer to the
8 complaint or to a cross-claim, or a reply to a counterclaim, within sixty days after service upon
9 the pleading in which the claim is asserted.
